        public void doGetAllPagesFromOffsetExample()
        Commenting out the getAllPages*() methods due to the potential for a large quantity of data retrieved at runtime. But if desired, this code can be uncommented and executed as part of these example methods. Be aware that these commented methods may take some time to run depending on the quantity of data, since all pages are retrieved.
